FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our finance app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How secure is my financial data?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: We use bank-level encryption and multi-factor authentication to ensure your financial data is always protected.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Can I link multiple bank accounts?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, you can easily link and manage multiple bank accounts, credit cards, and investment portfolios in one place.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is there a fee for using the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We offer both free and premium plans. The basic features are free, while advanced tools and insights are available in our premium subscription.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How does the budgeting feature work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Our app automatically categorizes your expenses and helps you set personalized budgets. You'll receive alerts when you're close to exceeding your limits.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I export my financial reports?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Absolutely! You can generate and export detailed financial reports in various formats, including PDF and Excel, for your records or tax purposes.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How secure is my financial data?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: We use bank-level encryption and security measures to ensure your financial data is always protected. Your privacy and security are our top priorities.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I link multiple bank accounts?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, you can easily link and manage multiple bank accounts, credit cards, and investment portfolios all in one place for a comprehensive view of your finances.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Is there a fee for using the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We offer both free and premium versions. The basic features are free, while advanced budgeting tools and personalized financial advice are available with our premium subscription.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How does the app help me budget?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our app automatically categorizes your expenses, tracks your spending habits, and provides customizable budgets. You'll receive alerts when you're nearing your limits and get insights to improve your financial health.
